troubleshoot & conclusion
=========================

-> ' if ' accept only Boolean value (or) Boolean statements
-> ' switch ' accepts numbers , char, strings
-> switch will not accept Boolean and decimal values
-> switch case should belongs to same type
-> switch case datatype and switch case input value should belongs to same data types
-> default case is optional is switch
-> break keyword is also optional
